                <head>No. 446<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>A letter of December 7 from Prime Minister <persName corresp="#p_CWS1"
                        >Churchill</persName> to President <persName corresp="#p_EDD1"
                        >Eisenhower</persName> and the President’s reply of December 14, both of
                    which pertain in part to China, are scheduled for publication in <ref
                        target="frus1952-54v06p1">volume VI</ref>.</p>
            </div>
